entries.title_d: You're being ambushed by Blacklight assassins. Defend yourself and eliminate the threat pilot!
entries.title: Endor system: Blacklights strike back!
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < Holy cow! We may be in over our head! The base is up ahead and the Blacklights are on to you! >
entries.complete: Brother Ezkiel: < Great job pilot, you showed those fools what a real pilot can do! >
